The command you ran:\
\
```bash\
psql "postgres://postgres:<PASSWORD>@127.0.0.1:5434/postgres" -c "\\l"\
```\
- Host: `127.0.0.1`\
- Port: `5434`\
- DB: `postgres`\
- Result: only\
  - `cloudsqladmin`\
  - `postgres`\
  - `template0`\
  - `template1`\
