```\
2. **Cloud SQL via proxy on 5433 (what your app uses)**  \
   Docs + scripts assume a Cloud SQL DB named `nexus_db`, accessed through the proxy:\
\
   - Proxy: `cloud-sql-proxy --port=5433 <INSTANCE_NAME>`\
   - App `DATABASE_URL` pattern:\
